  - Nomination, endorsements, disclosures and deadlines verify karein
  - Cost, timeline, limits and corrections ke saath manifesto publish karein
  - Candidate disclosure, conflict, interview and appeal records check karein
  - Multilingual, easy-read and accessible campaign media run karein
  - Small meetings, listening cards and consent-based follow-up yatra run karein
  - Equal-time sourced debate aur correction window complete karein
  - Issue-first federation ya spectacle convoy mein decision lein
  - Sources, caps, media invoices and vendor conflicts audit karein
  - Queue, accessibility, observer and result-form operations train karein
  - Neutral emergency, queue and evidence-handover safety drill karein
  - Corrections, promotion pause and result-acceptance statement activate karein
  - Independent 100-seat fictional national count aur result dekhein
